<add><ab facs="#facs_38_line_1576491052777_7910">ir </ab></add> etlıch beẏ ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l26">in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> venknuſʒe lıgen habt / . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . / daʒ Jr vns 
